        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
                <h2 class="margin-top-0 text-primary">x86 64bit Cores</h2>
                <br>
                <p class="large">Intel Avoton CPU offered great performance in their price range allowing for an efficient server for cloud purposes. They are an excellent alternative to ARM CPUs for applications which need more memory.</p>
                <p class="large">The Intel Avoton are systems on a chip (SoC). Due to their power and price we can pass on the savings.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                <img src="/libs/assets/laptop-rocket.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
